Number = {12},
Month = {JUN},
Abstract = {This paper compares the usability of various Apple MacBook Pro laptops
   were tested for basic machine learning research applications, including
   text-based, vision-based, and tabular data. Four tests/benchmarks were
   conducted using four different MacBook Pro models-M1, M1 Pro, M2, and M2
   Pro. A script written in Swift was used to train and evaluate four
   machine learning models using the Create ML framework, and the process
   was repeated three times. The script also measured performance metrics,
   including time results. The results were presented in tables, allowing
   for a comparison of the performance of each device and the impact of
   their hardware architectures.},
