   Mainas, Francesca; Golosio, Bruno, Univ Cagliari, Dept Phys, I-09042 Monserrato, Italy.
   Mainas, Francesca; Golosio, Bruno; Oliva, Piernicola, Natl Inst Nucl Phys INFN, Cagliari Div, I-09042 Monserrato, Italy.
