   Smerat, Aseel, Saveetha Inst Med \& Tech Sci, Saveetha Sch Engn, Dept Biosci, Chennai, India.
   Smerat, Aseel, Al Ahliyya Amman Univ, Fac Educ Sci, Amman, Jordan.
   Hosseinzadeh, Mehdi, Duy Tan Univ, Sch Comp Sci, Da Nang, Vietnam.
   Hosseinzadeh, Mehdi, Jadara Univ, Jadara Univ Res Ctr, Irbid, Jordan.
   Hosseinzadeh, Mehdi, Macquarie Univ, Ctr Appl AI, Sydney, Australia.
   Kim, Changgyun, Kangwon Natl Univ, Dept Elect \& AI Syst Engn, Samcheok, South Korea.
   Syafrudin, Muhammad; Fitriyani, Norma Latif, Sejong Univ, Dept Artificial Intelligence \& Data Sci, Seoul, South Korea.},
